.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, dancing, board-games, cooking
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, mexican, nigerian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the nigerian##1
6. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games | skydiving   | cooking | dancing |
| Nationality   | canadian      | mexican | turkish      | nigerian |

