2. the mexican is the person drinking juice##1
3. the french is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the italian is somewhere between the polish and the french##7
7. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta      | tea | juice     |
| Nationality   | polish    | italian | french   | mexican |

