.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, apricot, artichoke, pumpkin
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, russian, french, brazilian
1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the russian##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
4. the brazilian is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating artichoke##7
5. the french is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pumpkin    | broccoli   | apricot | artichoke  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | french | brazilian    | russian |

