.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, german, canadian
4 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, bird, frog
1. the brazilian is not the owner of the frog##6
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
3. the canadian is the owner of the bird##1
4. the german is somewhere between the canadian and the indian##7
5. the brazilian is on the left of the indian##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | german | brazilian | indian |
| Pet           | bird   | frog    | turtle       | cat  |

