.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, journalist, manager, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, electronic, blues, gospel
1. the photographer is not the fan of funk##6
2. the manager is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the photographer##3
4. the photographer is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
5. the manager is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the journalist##7
6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | electrician | photographer | manager | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | gospel         | blues      | funk | electronic            |

