3. the owner of the rabbit is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
