2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching drama movies and the fan of indie##2
6. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching drama movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
