.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, woodworking, baking
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, car, jet-ski
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | baking | cooking | rock-climbing | woodworking |
| Transport   | taxi   | jet-ski      | quad-bike        | car  |

