1. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
2. the fan of folk is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of electronic##7
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | electronic   | folk | blues |

