2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the helicopter##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage    | cola   | milk  | hot-chocolate  | sprite |
| Transport   | van | tram | scooter | helicopter    |

