.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, turtle, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, van, subway, helicopter
1. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | frog    | turtle | rabbit     | pony |
| Transport   | subway | helicopter  | van | trike |

 